{"tid":1044062,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"洛里斯：有點兒瘋狂","createTime":"2019-03-02T16:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T19:38:00.000Z","uid":199590,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"031ff8bc997a2fa355c727241484ee51805c1a0f","tid":1044062,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:03:08.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=6e57316a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】熱刺門將洛里斯在北倫敦打吡和波後，以瘋狂來形容比賽。<br />\n<br />\n「這場比賽有點兒瘋狂，雙方都最後都可以贏2:1，但對我們而言，經過艱難的1星期，這是很好的1分。」完場前擋出奧巴美揚12碼，令球隊幸保1的熱刺門將洛里斯（Hugo Lloris）賽後說：「所有事情都來得快，我從來保護自己後防隊友，但我也尊重球證的判決。」<br />\n<br />\n戲劇性一幕於完場前出現，奧巴美揚禁區內博得達雲臣山齊士犯規，但他親自主射被洛里斯擋出，錯過絕殺機會。熱刺終逼和阿仙奴不致3連敗，而賽後以61分穩守第3，阿仙奴得57分。<br />\n<br />\n為球隊射入扳平的哈利卡尼謂：「這是1分，我們原意想取3分，但如今終止連敗走勢。我們可以集中備戰多蒙特及修咸頓。」"},{"pid":"2eb2df54b4518e9b694beea64a599943547b87b1","tid":1044062,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:15:51.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"b6e3ac00eb352219973a8cd88d766d9e46e97452","tid":1044062,"uid":52006,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:22:10.000Z","msg":"冇球越位12碼你1分都冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0376887132b7c5bcf7d35904b30bac6a47eb181a","tid":1044062,"uid":36138,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"b6e3ac00eb352219973a8cd88d766d9e46e97452","tid":1044062,"uid":52006,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:22:10.000Z","msg":"冇球越位12碼你1分都冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:25:43.000Z","msg":"果球點會吹offside? 球例話係foul before offside offence"},{"pid":"11894f70a8788fe8fe233a968f2918fb096c3a5f","tid":1044062,"uid":57854,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0376887132b7c5bcf7d35904b30bac6a47eb181a","tid":1044062,"uid":36138,"like":3,"dislike":